title: #92Noon! Wobby/Florio/King/Spadaro and more LIVE from MOA!
description: PA, Nordo, and Wobby are LIVE at Radio Row inside the Mall of America! ProFootballTalk's Mike Florio, SI's Peter King, Eagles insider Dave Spadaro, and plenty of other guests join the kickoff to Super Bowl week on #92Noon!
